asFile

public java.io.File asFile(java.io.File source)
Cast the given source file (in any bucket) as a file in this bucket. No movement occurs, this just manipulates names.

NOTE: A side effect is for this bucket to be created if it doesn't yet exist AND the source file exists.

asDirectory

public java.io.File asDirectory(java.io.File dir)
Cast the given (arbitrary) bucket directory to this bucket's directory.

NOTE: A side effect is for this bucket's directory to be created if it doesn't yet exist AND the given directory exists.

claim

public java.io.File claim(java.io.File source)
Claim the given source file (in any bucket) into this bucket.

NOTE: The source file will be moved to this bucket if it exists.

delete

public void delete(java.io.File file)
Delete this bucket's version of the file (ok if in another bucket) if it exists.
